Dialogue: 5,0:01:50.13,0:01:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.50,0:01:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:52.55,0:01:54.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone's already here?
Dialogue: 5,0:01:55.38,0:01:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:56.80,0:01:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:58.22,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:59.59,0:02:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.97,0:02:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.93,0:02:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:02.89,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.48,0:02:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:06.81,0:02:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you looking at me like that?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:12.19,0:02:14.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.53,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Come over here, Tada Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.86,0:02:18.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's do this together.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.57,0:02:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We're hanging up these lights before the fourth years arrive.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:22.41,0:02:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't forget about these lanterns.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:28.62,0:02:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No! You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.79,0:02:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:31.63,0:02:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not scary.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:33.42,0:02:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you are!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.96,0:02:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You're acting weird!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.59,0:02:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing weird about us.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.22,0:02:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't get to go on our overnight trip,
Dialogue: 5,0:02:41.43,0:02:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,but let's have fun today to make up for it.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.89,0:02:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The president's connections got us this place too.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.02,0:02:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right? Isn't this fun?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:50.77,0:02:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,The Festival Club is so much fun, isn't it?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:56.98,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:00.15,0:03:01.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I've really, really missed you.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.49,0:03:08.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What have you been up to lately?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:08.50,0:03:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, lately... I... just, um...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:11.87,0:03:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,"Just"?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.13,0:03:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you can't help that, can you?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:18.30,0:03:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess you could say we see you and RoboGirl as... well...
Dialogue: 5,0:03:24.85,0:03:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,sort of like a fertilized egg.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:27.01,0:03:29.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.85,0:03:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Two life forms that have become one.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:32.85,0:03:34.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.15,0:03:39.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like you and RoboGirl were always one.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:40.24,0:03:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the genes that will carry our souls on to the next generation.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:43.99,0:03:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:47.16,0:03:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.75,0:03:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai isn't here?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:50.58,0:03:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Her?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she'd come here from home.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:55.17,0:03:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But forget about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:56.79,0:03:59.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she went home to Shizuoka?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:59.21,0:04:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't talk about it right after I told you to forget it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:02.01,0:04:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, what about you?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.89,0:04:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I mean {\i1}you guys{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.76,0:04:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, I really don't understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:10.52,0:04:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What I'm trying to say is...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:14.19,0:04:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We all want to include you and RoboGirl.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:20.74,0:04:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You get it, don't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:22.82,0:04:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.78,0:04:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.41,0:04:28.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:29.16,0:04:30.70,Default,,0,0,0,,It's {\i1}that{\i0}! Get it?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.66,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:34.29,0:04:37.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, just because you broke up with RoboGirl,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.67,0:04:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,neither of you should quit the club.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:41.21,0:04:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.59,0:04:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell us.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.84,0:04:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:45.05,0:04:49.26,Default,,0,0,0,,We've been calling and texting RoboGirl lately,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.26,0:04:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,but we can't get in touch with her.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:51.52,0:04:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when we called you,
Dialogue: 5,0:04:52.93,0:04:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,when we asked about RoboGirl, you gave vague answers.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.31,0:04:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that what it means?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.15,0:04:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:59.94,0:05:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:01.40,0:05:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if you're not a couple anymore, that doesn't mean your bond with us is lost.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.11,0:05:08.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, guys?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:08.62,0:05:09.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.58,0:05:12.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll soothe the pain of lost love!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.29,0:05:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:12.87,0:05:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's cheer up Tada Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:14.66,0:05:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.67,0:05:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:17.83,0:05:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.92,0:05:19.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.79,0:05:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}No, no, no!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada! Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:20.80,0:05:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why would you assume that?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.67,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Tada! Banri!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:23.71,0:05:24.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Kouko and I are...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.42,0:05:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:29.85,0:05:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,RoboGirl!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:31.18,0:05:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,RoboGirl's here!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.97,0:05:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,RoboGirl's returned from the heart-repair factory!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:36.98,0:05:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's give a warm welcome to the nearly broken RoboGirl.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:40.90,0:05:42.36,Default,,0,0,0,,RoboGirl!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.57,0:05:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on? What?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:45.15,0:05:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that! You've got the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:47.78,0:05:48.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell us.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:48.95,0:05:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,We understand.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:49.99,0:05:51.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, you don't understand!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.08,0:05:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We didn't break up!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.37,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:57.25,0:05:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this is stupid.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.33,0:06:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,We wasted our time trying to be nice to them.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.46,0:06:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We were really worried about what we'd do if you quit.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.76,0:06:06.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:07.13,0:06:08.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:10.09,0:06:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw, don't blame them.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:12.26,0:06:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not their fault.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.47,0:06:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you're the one to blame!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:17.69,0:06:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You were the first to assume they broke up.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.90,0:06:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys said you were sure about it too!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:25.69,0:06:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to blame us?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.86,0:06:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your fault for jumping to conclusions!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.28,0:06:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}We might have come dangerously close to it, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.12,0:06:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't close at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:33.03,0:06:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't even within the range of "close."
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.83,0:06:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:38.75,0:06:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.08,0:06:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I just thought you look good in your yukata.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.21,0:06:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This? I made it this year.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.17,0:06:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I decided I wanted to go, so I {\i1}will{\i0} go and see fireworks with you this summer!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.47,0:06:53.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It rained the other day, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:53.39,0:06:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:54.60,0:06:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:56.47,0:06:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I just got word.
