Dialogue: 5,0:06:58.23,0:07:02.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Former president Hoshino-senpai is coming here today.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.69,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously? Hosshi-san's coming?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he wouldn't come if he couldn't find a job.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That means...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:09.07,0:07:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,...he found work!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.45,0:07:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,He'd been looking really gloomy.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:13.78,0:07:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Let's celebrate with everything we have!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.24,0:07:18.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.08,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, it's been a while!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:28.97,0:07:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosshi-senpai!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.30,0:07:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Your legendary pirouette is so cool.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:32.64,0:07:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it? Isn't it cool?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:34.55,0:07:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, this place is awesome.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.60,0:07:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, guys.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:38.10,0:07:40.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We should've helped.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:40.35,0:07:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be ridiculous.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:42.10,0:07:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.19,0:07:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hosshi-senpai.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:44.77,0:07:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations on your employment!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:46.77,0:07:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:48.82,0:07:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:49.86,0:07:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Now all the fourth years have found jobs.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.57,0:07:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:55.91,0:07:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:00.91,0:08:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't actually found a job yet...
Dialogue: 5,0:08:04.38,0:08:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,you might say.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:10.46,0:08:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted a change of pace.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:12.76,0:08:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I came.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:15.34,0:08:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:18.14,0:08:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.64,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:21.35,0:08:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this mood in the air?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:27.31,0:08:30.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong with me, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:30.15,0:08:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Those guys out there in the world are lousy judges of character!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.82,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I know what you mean.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:33.03,0:08:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:34.11,0:08:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, drink some more.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:35.16,0:08:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}In any case, I'm glad you're all okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.74,0:08:39.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka-chan's injury is better now, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:39.95,0:08:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, completely.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.83,0:08:45.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry for making you worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:45.04,0:08:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:46.33,0:08:49.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though I was at home, I felt uneasy.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:49.96,0:08:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, how did you hear about the accident?
Dialogue: 5,0:08:52.72,0:08:55.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you know, from people.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.85,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm quite relieved, though.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.85,0:09:02.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worried until I finally saw you.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,It was worth coming back just to see you two.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:19.62,0:09:20.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:20.62,0:09:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:21.79,0:09:26.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we ever light fireworks together before I lost my memory?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:33.76,0:09:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You were in the same class for all three years of high school, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:38.93,0:09:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:40.10,0:09:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Before I fell off that bridge.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:42.97,0:09:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You were both on the track team, weren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:45.73,0:09:48.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You must've looked so cool, Linda-senpai.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:49.56,0:09:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,About those fireworks...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.90,0:09:54.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a look at your left leg, Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:55.07,0:09:56.57,Default,,0,0,0,,My left leg?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:59.57,0:10:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a burn scar.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:01.70,0:10:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,In the summer of our second year, when we lit fireworks on the track team's overnight trip,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.75,0:10:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,a bottle rocket fell over and struck you.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:09.21,0:10:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:10.71,0:10:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I remember!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:12.29,0:10:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hurt myself protecting you!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:15.71,0:10:17.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This scar is a badge of honor!
Dialogue: 5,0:10:17.55,0:10:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:20.68,0:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I ran away quickly, but you were stupidly slow to run.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:25.93,0:10:29.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We got in a lot of trouble with our adviser afterward.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:29.98,0:10:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:31.52,0:10:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:33.19,0:10:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all in the past.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:36.53,0:10:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Banri,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:38.82,0:10:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,are you going home for summer break?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:42.03,0:10:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.20,0:10:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,My parents have been pushing me to go.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:47.54,0:10:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, that's how it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:50.17,0:10:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,If you happen to see Banri while you're back home,
Dialogue: 5,0:10:53.04,0:10:54.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope you'll hang out with him.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:54.71,0:10:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:58.05,0:11:02.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I wasn't going to bring this up,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:03.72,0:11:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,but can I say something?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:09.77,0:11:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A high school class reunion?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.81,0:11:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, next week.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.81,0:11:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Our class is holding a reunion.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.99,0:11:22.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I was sure you wouldn't want to come, so I wasn't going to tell you,
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.74,0:11:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but do you want to stop by?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:26.83,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I won't force you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:30.29,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just... everyone's worried about you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:34.34,0:11:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,If you show them you're fine, I think they'll be really happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to tell you that.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.47,0:11:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Senpai.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri will attend.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:45.55,0:11:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.60,0:11:47.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You will, won't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:47.93,0:11:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You won't?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.77,0:11:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You will, right? Of course you will.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.19,0:11:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'll go.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:58.82,0:12:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the class reunion.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I do something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.50,0:12:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for making the decision for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.62,0:12:14.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I make trouble for you again?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I've decided to stop running from my past.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:19.71,0:12:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:22.84,0:12:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, I'm nervous.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:25.34,0:12:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The person everyone wants to see is the Tada Banri from before I lost my memory.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a completely different person from who I am now.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.48,0:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,When they see me, they might think,\N"Who is this guy?"
Dialogue: 5,0:12:39.11,0:12:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,"You're not the one we want to see."
Dialogue: 5,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"We want to see the old Banri."
Dialogue: 5,0:12:44.74,0:12:46.99,Default,,0,0,0,,They might think something like that.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:48.24,0:12:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,You told me the other day that I'd abandoned my friends and family and run away.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:54.21,0:12:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:56.33,0:12:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry about that.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.84,0:13:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you don't remember them.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:02.26,0:13:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't have...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.34,0:13:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:04.72,0:13:06.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you said it.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.89,0:13:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,It helped me decide to face my past.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:12.77,0:13:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go see my classmates.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:15.14,0:13:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't help what they think about me.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:17.90,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll apologize for making them worry and thank them.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:23.74,0:13:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why it is.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:25.95,0:13:30.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I'll finally get to see the whole Banri.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.95,0:13:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The whole me?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:32.45,0:13:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I think I couldn't really accept you before.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.67,0:13:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I only saw the Banri I wanted to see.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:42.92,0:13:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't accept that there were people
Dialogue: 5,0:13:46.63,0:13:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,who knew a Banri that I didn't know.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.97,0:13:54.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I must've been jealous.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:55.93,0:13:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,But what you said...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.98,0:14:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"I'll do my best, so you do your best too."
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.32,0:14:04.44,Default,,0,0,0,,"Don't get out of the car."
Dialogue: 5,0:14:05.69,0:14:09.11,Default,,0,0,0,,When you said that, I realized I loved you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:10.07,0:14:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I realized it was fine for me to keep loving you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.62,0:14:18.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I love you because you're you.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:18.96,0:14:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm happy that you're whole.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:22.67,0:14:28.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't care if there are sides of you I don't know or don't like.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.47,0:14:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,If that's who you are, that's fine.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:30.93,0:14:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you're whole, that's enough for me.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:36.93,0:14:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm struggling because I've lost sight of my whole self.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.23,0:14:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,That's part of who you are too.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.99,0:14:50.70,Default,,0,0,0,,So go see your past with your own eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:51.70,0:14:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See for yourself the Banri you've forgotten,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:54.24,0:14:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,the you before you met me,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.50,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,and then tell me about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:23.56,0:15:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I open this box?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:25.94,0:15:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.78,0:15:29.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but could you take that box to the corner over there?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:30.40,0:15:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's full of fragile stuff, so be careful.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:33.74,0:15:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a real slave driver, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:36.45,0:15:37.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.87,0:15:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaga-san, you're staying here tonight, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:41.87,0:15:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:42.62,0:15:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll take until nighttime to finish putting things away.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:45.29,0:15:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you're going to make me work until then?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:49.21,0:15:50.01,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.01,0:15:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,But isn't that why you came here?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:52.76,0:15:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.97,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no intention of helping you move.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a little curious, so I came to take a look.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:00.64,0:16:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,When I heard your apartment wasn't what you imagined,
Dialogue: 5,0:16:02.77,0:16:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I'd come laugh at you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:04.81,0:16:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why you brought an apron?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:07.11,0:16:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, let's get this done quickly.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:09.74,0:16:12.91,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be the first one to stay over!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not staying!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:15.57,0:16:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Absolutely not. Not even if it kills me.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:17.03,0:16:19.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't stay over even if the world ends!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Kaga-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:25.17,0:16:26.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:26.96,0:16:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want me to guess what you're thinking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:30.59,0:16:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Do whatever you want.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:32.67,0:16:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You're thinking about Banri, aren't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:34.68,0:16:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You're wondering what he's up to in Shizuoka right now.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:39.52,0:16:41.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You're amazing.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.93,0:16:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you fall in love, you really love that person through thick and thin.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:47.23,0:16:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't everyone like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:50.07,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,No, they're not.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:51.86,0:16:55.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a lot of respect for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.11,0:16:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:56.49,0:16:59.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what did you...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:01.04,0:17:03.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're just pretending to sleep.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:05.67,0:17:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.17,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, you're not leaving yet?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.59,0:17:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'm staying until the first train.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:16.13,0:17:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Once the trains start running, I'll get on a bullet train.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:19.56,0:17:22.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going home again?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:22.31,0:17:25.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I meant to go right back home in the first place,
Dialogue: 5,0:17:25.14,0:17:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but I was suddenly asked to work here, and that delayed my plans a day.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:28.90,0:17:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to see the two underclassmen too.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:31.69,0:17:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, did I do something I shouldn't have?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:35.86,0:17:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I made you worry by telling you about the accident.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.49,0:17:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.62,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad you told me.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:43.33,0:17:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:44.71,0:17:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:47.75,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, do you need some help?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:50.34,0:17:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that's okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:51.96,0:17:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm finished.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:54.97,0:17:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Um, how long are you going to be at home?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the end of summer break, I think.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:00.68,0:18:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a class reunion,
Dialogue: 5,0:18:02.43,0:18:05.39,Default,,0,0,0,,and I have plans to hang out with some friends after that.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:05.39,0:18:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,A reunion, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:07.06,0:18:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:09.15,0:18:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have any plans like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:11.77,0:18:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,None yet.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:13.57,0:18:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri's gone home too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:15.78,0:18:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,With fewer friends around, I don't have much to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.61,0:18:21.58,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\1c&H595950&\fnPF Ronda Seven\b0\fscx49\fscy49\fax0.16\fry12\pos(997.5,595.5)\frz18.5}Tokyo
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.74,0:18:21.58,golden teim,,0,0,0,,{\blur0.9\1c&H595950&\fnPF Ronda Seven\b0\fscx49\fscy49\frz17.5\fax0.2\fry5\pos(1402.567,479.615)}Shizuoka
Dialogue: 5,0:18:19.57,0:18:21.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Linda-senpai, you're from Shizuoka?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:21.95,0:18:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:23.62,0:18:27.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri said he's from Shizuoka too.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:27.29,0:18:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe you'll run into Banri somewhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:30.38,0:18:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,That won't happen!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.25,0:18:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Shizuoka's a big place.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:36.21,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.59,0:18:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:38.43,0:18:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:39.30,0:18:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it back.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.30,0:18:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:41.39,0:18:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you doing this?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:44.26,0:18:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think I'm doing this?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:51.61,0:18:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm going back to my apartment first.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:53.61,0:18:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:58.65,0:19:00.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Three is fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:00.82,0:19:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but make them all different flavors.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:03.58,0:19:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,And where's the restroom?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:07.20,0:19:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:11.63,0:19:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad Kaga-san's feeling better.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:16.09,0:19:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:18.72,0:19:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:19.63,0:19:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish I could've seen Oka-chan too.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:21.97,0:19:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess she can't help it.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:23.35,0:19:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,She said she's not done unpacking.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:26.06,0:19:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something bothering you today?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:31.31,0:19:33.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't say it's bothering me, but...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:34.48,0:19:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Banri's from Shizuoka, isn't he?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:38.19,0:19:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know what high school he attended?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:40.15,0:19:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:41.20,0:19:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You know he doesn't really talk about his past.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it...
Dialogue: 5,0:19:46.08,0:19:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe he doesn't want to \Nremember because of his accident.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:50.66,0:19:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Accident?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:51.75,0:19:53.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the one the other day?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:53.25,0:19:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,No, not that.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:54.50,0:19:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:55.21,0:19:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You haven't heard, Yana-san?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:56.88,0:19:59.09,Default,,0,0,0,,About when Banri fell from a bridge and got badly hurt?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:59.59,0:20:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Badly hurt?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:01.09,0:20:05.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We were tricked by some weird cult and taken to their campsite.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Banri told us about it then.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.56,0:20:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He fell from a bridge and was hospitalized for a while.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:12.10,0:20:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, he said, "I'm interested in religion because I've had that experience."
Dialogue: 5,0:20:16.73,0:20:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,"No one else is interested, so let them go."
Dialogue: 5,0:20:19.99,0:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that really true, though?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:23.03,0:20:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought it was a lie too.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:25.87,0:20:30.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I assumed he made something up so we could escape. But...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:31.46,0:20:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,when we went to the beach the other day, I saw a faint scar.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:35.50,0:20:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Around here.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:37.29,0:20:39.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I pretended not to notice,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.05,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but maybe what he said at that camp was true.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.26,0:20:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He said a bunch of other things too.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.51,0:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, other things?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:46.80,0:20:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't know how much is true and how much is false.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:51.27,0:20:56.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, we shouldn't look into it too much if he doesn't want to talk about it.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:56.19,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for waiting.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:03.82,0:21:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,These look delicious.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:05.70,0:21:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Take whichever one you want.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.03,0:21:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,It's on me...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.66,0:21:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,because I made you guys worry.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:10.83,0:21:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a big heart, Kaga-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:13.21,0:21:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:14.04,0:21:16.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying about my nice body?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.58,0:21:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm kidding, I'm kidding.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:17.58,0:21:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You're very thin.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:18.67,0:21:20.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kouko, did you know?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.75,0:21:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Know what?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.17,0:21:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That Banri was hospitalized.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:24.09,0:21:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Yana-san!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.97,0:21:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knows?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.60,0:21:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, take a spoon.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:32.35,0:21:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks...
Dialogue: 5,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Mitsuo.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:36.52,0:21:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll dig in, then.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:39.15,0:21:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Go ahead.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:40.82,0:21:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right. Kaga-san, how was Oka-chan's place?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:44.03,0:21:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You stayed over, didn't you?
Dialogue: 5,0:21:45.11,0:21:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:46.20,0:21:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, she even made me help her move.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:50.49,0:21:52.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You were doing work? Sounds cool.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:52.49,0:21:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
